gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 113, Wizards 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Wizards, 113-104. Nikola Jokic recorded a season-high 42 points, to go along with 12 rebounds and eight assists for the Nuggets, with Jamal Murray adding 19 points, seven assists, and five rebounds in the victory. Tyus Jones tallied 15 points and 13 assists for the Wizards in the defeat. The Nuggets improve to 30-14, while the Wizards fall to 7-35.
